# User Guide for SkillSync

## Getting Started

Welcome to SkillSync! This guide will help you navigate through the features and functionalities of the SkillSync platform.

### 1. Creating an Account

To get started, you need to create an account:

- Visit the registration page.
- Fill in the required details such as name, email, and password.
- Click on the "Register" button.
- Verify your email address through the link sent to your inbox.

### 2. Logging In

Once you have created an account, you can log in:

- Go to the login page.
- Enter your registered email and password.
- Click on the "Login" button.

### 3. Setting Up Your Profile

After logging in, it's important to set up your profile:

- Navigate to the Profile section.
- Fill in your personal information, including your skills and career interests.
- Upload your resume if applicable.
- Save your changes.

### 4. Exploring Career Paths

SkillSync offers various career paths tailored to your interests:

- Go to the Career Analysis page.
- Browse through the suggested career paths based on your profile.
- Click on a career path to view detailed information and recommended skills.

### 5. Learning and Development

To enhance your skills, you can access learning resources:

- Visit the Learning Path section.
- Explore courses and materials recommended for your chosen career path.
- Enroll in courses directly from the platform.

### 6. Job Board

SkillSync provides a job board to help you find job opportunities:

- Navigate to the Job Board section.
- Filter jobs based on your preferences (location, job type, etc.).
- Apply for jobs directly through the platform.

### 7. Dashboard Overview

Your dashboard provides a summary of your progress:

- View your learning progress and completed courses.
- Check job matches based on your profile.
- Track your career development milestones.

### 8. Support and Feedback

If you encounter any issues or have feedback:

- Visit the Support section.
- Submit a ticket or contact our support team via email.

## Conclusion

SkillSync is designed to help you navigate your career journey effectively. Make the most of the features available and take charge of your professional development!